column2: Based on the information provided in the document, the new investee companies that Info Edge (India) Limited invested in during the financial year ended March 31, 2023, are Techinvest technologies Pvt Ltd, Redstart Labs (India) Limited, and Zwayam Digital Private Limited. These companies were acquired by the company during the financial year ended March 31, 2023. Additionally, the company also invested in Axilly Labs Private Limited during the same financial year.
